```

Use [File.stream!/3](https://hexdocs.pm/elixir/File.html#stream!/3) to read each line of `multi-line.txt` and convert it to a list of lines using [Enum.to_list/1](https://hexdocs.pm/elixir/Enum.html#to_list/1).

```elixir
